Based on FEINCMS tree editor (see http://www.feinheit.ch/, 
                                  https://github.com/matthiask/feincms)

Usage:
-----
 * install django-sakkada
 * import MpttTreeAdmin (AjaxBoolAdmin), and ajax_boolean from sakkada.admin.mptt_tree
 * set MpttTreeAdmin (AjaxBoolAdmin) as class of admin model
 * define ajax_boolean params for required fields
 * copy templates (admin/mptt_tree/*) to your application template folder
 * copy static (mptt_tree and jquery) to your application static folder

Example usage:
-------------
from sakkada.admin.mptt_tree import MpttTreeAdmin, AjaxBoolAdmin, ajax_boolean

class SomeTreeAdmin(MpttTreeAdmin, admin.ModelAdmin):
    ajax_active = ajax_boolean('active', _('is active?'))

class SomeFlatAdmin(AjaxBoolAdmin, admin.ModelAdmin):
    ajax_active = ajax_boolean('active', _('is active?'))